---
title: Curry-Spiced Grilling Cheese Bowls with Rice, Oven-Roasted Kale & Garlicky White Sauce
description: In the HF Kitchen, we’re pretty obsessed with grilling cheese and its ability to fry up golden on the outside melty within. For tonight’s version, you’ll coat the cheese in curry powder and olive oil before pan-searing. All that golden goodness is served over bowls of jasmine rice, sautéed bell pepper and onion with honey, and oven-roasted kale. Finally, a drizzle of creamy garlic sauce tops things off with a lemony tang.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/curry-spiced-grilling-cheese-bowls-09432ada.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/curry-spiced-grilling-cheese-bowls-62f29dbe033390b247025ff9-8db94b6b.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
