  carbohydrates: 75 g
  sugar: 15 g
  protein: 29 g
  fiber: 7 g
  sodium: 850 mg
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/curry-spiced-grilling-cheese-bowls-62f29dbe033390b247025ff9
author: HelloFresh
